    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Discretization error factor achieved Gradation 3, exceeding the Gradation 2 requirement. Experimental comparison demonstrates RH < 1 at all 5 CPB operating points with mean absolute relative error of 8.3%, within the pre-specified 15% acceptance threshold. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
